song_name: Til The Sun Comes Back Around
version_description: Took both versions of the song (the original, kinda acoustic, and the movie version) to make this chord sheet for someone to play solo. There's a good deal of digital instruments doing a single tone below Chris' voice in the beggining, I've added the chords that comes after to make it more dynamic and in pair with how he played it live. UPDATE: UG user mkeymont pointed out that a few verses had the wrong lyrics. After watching a video of Chris performing it live (https://youtu.be/RM_v6aXP1Ls), I've decided to look for the official version, but it is nowhere to be found, not even at Chris' own website. So, I've decided to add some of mkeymont's suggestions and, maybe, now it is closer to the actual one.
Includes all the different chords and inversions as well as the guitar part's chord additions to the original chart.

song_name: Whats So Funny Bout Peace Love And Understanding

version_description: Transcribed from the YouTube live acoustic versions I've seen.

I've compared all the previous versions with the actual song and none is (for me) as accurate as this one.  I always miss some chord changes in the others, that is what I included here. Also corrected strange chords, a few mistakes in the lyrics, and cleared the structure.
Chords extracted from video of live performance, should be accurate.
This is the version I use anyway, Drop D, Bar and Power-chords.
